{"tid":1365714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若果今次死係元朗","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:10:00.000Z","uid":265197,"like":430,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6ec734217385ca216f5135d92a20f129ef73d0","tid":1365714,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"出賣港人仍面不改容嘅貪官污吏<br />\n故意放任老弱婦孺被襲擊仍嬉皮笑臉嘅香港警察<br />\n受人錢財傷天害理蝦女人打老人嘅黑社會<br />\n全部等天收<br />\n<br />\n關二哥在上<br />\n若我今次係元朗會被打死<br />\n我會以我嘅血、汗、淚、餘下未用嘅壽命同福祉、我嘅所有<br />\n詛咒呢批不仁不義嘅狗官、香港警察、黑幫<br />\n家無寧日<br />\n百病纏身<br />\n生生世世<br />\n子子孫孫<br />\n不得好死<br />\n懇求關二哥<br />\n將呢批不忠不孝不仁不義嘅狗賊<br />\n全部一個都不能放過<br />\n立此為誓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知係連登講有無用<br />\n我唔知咁樣發誓會唔會折福折壽<br />\n但我只知生為香港人，死為香港鬼<br />\n每一句都係我真心說話<br />\n願香港早日太平盛世"},{"pid":"5e5b4b335738693628fb269b2f6015eaf1f74459","tid":1365714,"uid":142217,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"安全為上呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ce93ab20c0fa99b3afb035bd96bcc8eb8a0bc0","tid":1365714,"uid":116171,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">點計都唔會係我哋死先</span><br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"925b5378011ffcac776e094df051b1cebef46422","tid":1365714,"uid":266879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"快學  當你被拖走時如何掙脫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365653</a>"},{"pid":"b7314824588514b2b075ec249bc93f4a37f4ca7d","tid":1365714,"uid":265197,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5e5b4b335738693628fb269b2f6015eaf1f74459","tid":1365714,"uid":142217,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"安全為上呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"我其實都好驚好擔心<br />\n但我仲驚輸比佢地<